01:07:00,977 --> 01:07:05,977
想い出たちを彩るように
To color our memories

803
01:07:06,477 --> 01:07:11,177
夜空に咲いた花火が
The fireworks blooming in the night sky

804
01:07:11,977 --> 01:07:16,977
色鮮やかに輝いてた
Were shining vividly

805
01:07:17,577 --> 01:07:22,477
ずっと…一緒にいたいよ
I want to be with you... forever

806
01:07:22,977 --> 01:07:27,977
来年もまたこんな風に
Next year, in this same way again

807
01:07:28,677 --> 01:07:33,377
笑い合いたいって思うから
Because I want us to laugh together

808
01:07:33,877 --> 01:07:38,977
線香花火に願うんだ
I make a wish on a sparkler

809
01:07:39,677 --> 01:07:44,377
「ずっとずっと続いて」
"Let it last forever and ever"

810
01:07:45,077 --> 01:07:46,977
きっと　きっと
Surely, surely

811
01:07:47,077 --> 01:07:50,177
叶う
It will come true

812
01:08:22,192 --> 01:08:23,807
お、ライブ無事終わった？
Oh, is the live over safely?

813
01:08:23,877 --> 01:08:26,677
よしよし、今のうちにクリスタルをっと…
Good, good, while I can, I'll take the crystals...

814
01:08:31,077 --> 01:08:33,377
あっはっは。これで来年のサマーも…
Ahahaha. With this, next year's Summer will also...

815
01:08:33,427 --> 01:08:35,507
あれ、マリンさん。もうライブは終わりましたよ。
Oh, Marine-san. The live is already over, you know.

816
01:08:35,577 --> 01:08:35,977
えっ！？
What!?

817
01:08:36,577 --> 01:08:37,877
あ、これ、その…
Ah, this is, well...

818
01:08:37,977 --> 01:08:39,677
あぁ〜〜！
Aaa~~!

819
01:08:49,177 --> 01:08:51,677
同じ未来を見ていたい
I want to see the same future

820
01:08:51,777 --> 01:08:54,177
あの夢手にした
I held that dream in my hands

821
01:08:54,477 --> 01:08:58,677
それぞれ誓った　ここで
Each of us made a vow, right here

822
01:08:59,577 --> 01:09:02,177
走り出そう
Let's start running

823
01:09:14,377 --> 01:09:17,677
どこ見ても真っ暗な場所に芽生えてた
It had sprouted in a place that was pitch black no matter where I looked

824
01:09:18,877 --> 01:09:22,977
ほんの小さな希望にこの瞳奪われた
My eyes were captivated by just a tiny bit of hope

825
01:09:26,477 --> 01:09:29,977
不安で揺れる心をうまくチューニングして
Tuning my heart that's swaying with anxiety

826
01:09:30,977 --> 01:09:35,377
ほんの小さな勇気を振り絞っていたよ
I was squeezing out just a tiny bit of courage

827
01:09:37,877 --> 01:09:41,477
諦めの文字でリミットして進む
Moving forward by limiting myself with the word "giving up"

828
01:09:42,377 --> 01:09:44,577
苦しい時も
Even during painful times

829
01:09:44,677 --> 01:09:46,877
もう私は
I am no longer

830
01:09:46,977 --> 01:09:49,377
独りじゃないから
alone anymore

831
01:09:52,177 --> 01:09:54,777
だからもっと夢追いかけたい
So I want to chase my dreams even more

832
01:09:54,877 --> 01:09:57,377
ワクワク止まらない
This excitement won't stop

833
01:09:57,577 --> 01:10:00,177
騒ごう
Let's make some noise

834
01:10:00,189 --> 01:10:01,389
超えて...
Go beyond...

835
01:10:01,439 --> 01:10:03,689
世界に見せてあげる
We'll show the world

836
01:10:03,689 --> 01:10:06,089
アクセル踏んでみたい
I want to step on the gas

837
01:10:06,089 --> 01:10:08,589
後悔なんてさせない
We won't let you have any regrets

838
01:10:08,589 --> 01:10:10,889
それぞれ違った
With our each unique...

839
01:10:10,889 --> 01:10:13,089
鼓動で
...heartbeats,

840
01:10:13,089 --> 01:10:15,689
走れ GO!
Run now, GO!

841
01:10:41,589 --> 01:11:10,189
ホロライブ・サマー2022に
ご参加ありがとうございました！
Thank you for participating in
Hololive Summer 2022!

